Headline: On GPS: Coronavirus Outbreak a "Big Test" for China
Article_Body: Anna Fifield, Beijing Bureau Chief for the Washington Post, Rana Foroohar, CNN Global Economic Analyst and Dr. Colleen Kraft, MD, Associate Chief Medical Officer at Emory University Hospital discuss the impact the Coronavirus is having on China. Fifield tells Fareed the country remains very much on shut down and the government is extremely concerned that the virus will cause a major economic hit as it faces many hurdles to resume some sense of normality.
